---
import HubLayout from '../layouts/HubLayout.astro';
---

<HubLayout title="Terms of Service — MyToolboxHub" description="Terms of Service for MyToolboxHub. Free, client-side utility suite for developers.">
  <div class="relative pt-8 pb-16 sm:pt-12 sm:pb-24 overflow-hidden mt-6 sm:mt-10 mb-12 sm:mb-16">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute top-1/4 right-1/3 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-accent/6 rounded-full blur-[100px]"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
      
      <!-- Heading -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-text-primary mb-4">
          Terms of <span class="text-accent">Service</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Effective Date: June 15, 2026. Clear, simple rules for utilizing our toolbox.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Glass Card Content -->
      <div class="glass p-8 sm:p-12 rounded-2xl space-y-8 prose prose-invert max-w-none">
        
        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-accent rounded-full"></span>
            1. Terms Acceptance
          </h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed text-sm">
            By visiting or using MyToolboxHub, you agree to comply with and be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, you must cease using the website immediately.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-accent rounded-full"></span>
            2. Allowed Use & Scope
          </h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed text-sm">
            MyToolboxHub provides web-based tools for code formatting, color conversion, hash generation, and general developers' productivity.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-text-secondary space-y-2">
            <li>You may use the tools for personal, academic, or commercial programming/design purposes.</li>
            <li>No scraper bots, automated spiders, or API abuse scripts should overload the hosting environment or package bundle deliveries.</li>
            <li>You are responsible for any keys, passwords, or data blocks you generate and utilize.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-accent rounded-full"></span>
            3. Disclaimer of Warranties
          </h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed text-sm">
            MyToolboxHub is provided <strong class="text-text-primary">"as is"</strong> and <strong class="text-text-primary">"as available"</strong>, without warranty of any kind, express or implied. While we strive to make tools accurate and secure:
          </p>
          <div class="bg-surface/50 border border-border-subtle p-4 rounded-xl text-xs text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            We do not warrant that tools will run error-free, uninterrupted, or that calculations (e.g., regex matching, database mock schemas) are 100% compliant with your custom parser guidelines. Use outputs at your own risk.
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-accent rounded-full"></span>
            4. Limitation of Liability
          </h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed text-sm">
            In no event shall MyToolboxHub or its creators be liable for any damages, losses, or costs arising out of your use, inability to use, or reliance on any output from these tools.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3">
          <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-6 bg-accent rounded-full"></span>
            5. Modifications to Terms
          </h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed text-sm">
            We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. Any changes will be updated on this page with an updated revision date.
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</HubLayout>
